messages.message: Hi Turkey! We don't overlap too much but it's always good to have an early line of communication in the south. Best of luck this game! ~N~ ~N~ Do you think you'll be opening against Russia?
Hmm, doubtful. I'm going to play neutral at the start, I think.
Looks like a pretty successful neutral start for you! Looks like Italy is going to go after France which is interesting
